code: import axios from"axios";export const deleteUser=async userId=>{try{const token=localStorage.getItem('token');const response=await axios.delete("https://api-mumul.site/v1/oauth/user/secession/".concat(userId),{headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json',Accept:'application/json',Authorization:'Bearer '+token}});localStorage.removeItem('token');return response.data;}catch(e){console.error('deletUser Error: ',e.message);}};
